    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to list this beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s a total gem and looks like it literally just rolled off the showroom floor! It has been incredibly well-loved and babied\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found. The interior is spotless and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for something that's in truly pristine, top-tier condition, this is the one for you! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
