      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional E46 M3, powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This specimen is mechanically superlative, featuring a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory variable M differential lock that remains tight and responsive. The chassis is reinforced at the subframe to ensure structural rigidity, and the VANOS unit has been meticulously serviced to maintain peak volumetric efficiency. Every suspension component, from the MacPherson struts to the multi-link rear, retains factory-spec geometry. This is an uncompromising, high-revving analog masterpiece with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 44800.0,
