      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade specimen that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like factory finish protected by a professional ceramic coating; there are no swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new, with premium leather that remains matte and supple, free of any bolster wear or creasing. Every technological feature and interior control operates with crisp, factory precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, supported by a complete, documented service history from authorized centers. The alloy wheels are flawless, wrapped in high-performance tires with near-full tread. This is an uncompromising example for the most discerning enthusiast who demands a showroom-quality experience.",
